# Build artefacts (lead-dot AND no-dot variants both seen in zig)
**/zig-cache/
**/.zig-cache/
**/zig-out/
**/.zig-out/
**/node_modules/
**/.cache/
**/_build/
**/target/
**/dist/

# Idris2 type-check output. Always emitted as `build/` DIRECTLY under an `abi/`
# dir, so this pattern is precise: it does NOT touch the legitimate
# `cross-cutting/build/` category (the Build-Server-Protocol cartridges).
**/abi/build/
*.ttc
*.ttm
*.ibc

# OS junk
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~

# Local env
.env.local
*.local.json

# Cartridge-side runtime
**/*.log

# Deno per-adapter lockfiles (regenerated on demand)
**/deno.lock
